Class DSPRoomSet

java.lang.Object
  DSPRoomSet

public class DSPRoomSet
extends java.lang.Object

COPYRIGHT (C) 2005 Rob Bauer. All Rights Reserved.

DSPRoomSet represents an object used in the Dijkstra's Shortest Path algorithm. While locating the shortest path, the room and its "cost" to get to it must be tracked. This object keeps track of this data.

Version:
1.0 2005-NOV-14
Author:
Rob Bauer
